name: No hay tiempo para la vergüenza
original_name: No hay tiempo para la vergüenza
overview: Follows the life and misadeventures of the eccentric fashion designer Santiago Artemis.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Back from a grueling overseas trip, Santiago needs an idea for his new collection. Meanwhile, he attends to a gay couple about to wed, and a rock star.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: As Santiago goes back to his hometown in the southern-most tip of Argentina to be recognized as an outstanding citizen, he remembers his roots.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: The trip home has Santiago brimming with ideas but also wracked with stress: The collection is behind, clients keep calling, and Luis makes a decision.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: To Santiago's surprise, his favorite singer, Brazilian diva Xuxa, calls him for a dress. He's still dealing with the collection but can't pass this up.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Santiago spends his time going from collaborator to collaborator to finish his collection, with brief stops to see his therapists -- and go on dates!

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: The collection is finally set for the runway and Santiago is both elated and a wreck. The lines are out the door, his mother's there, and he's ready.
